('92709','31927','5','Finca for horse lovers in Arta '),
('92710','31928','5','Only 5 minutes drive from Arta away is this very well maintained villa, situated in Finca style on a small hill with panoramic views. The plot of just under 22,000 is ideal for keeping horses. It is equipped with a paddock (20x40m), outlet coupling, some pastures, stables and 4 large horse boxes. \r\nIn the main house, with approx 350m² of living space, has a living-dining room with open fitted kitchen, utility room, laundry room and guest toilet. On the 1st floor there is the master bedroom with dressing room and bathroom, 2 bedrooms, 1 bathroom and various sun terraces. \r\nA separate guest apartment (55m ²) with living-dining room, kitchenette, bedroom and bathroom is available for guests or can be used for holiday letting. The house is surrounded on 3 sides with covered and open terraces, as well a the pool with pavilion to relax. \r\nThe excellent facilities includes: marble floors with gas / water under floor heating, air conditioning h / c, fireplace and wood double glazed windows.\r\n\r\n'),
